%header
  %h1 Submit
%hr  

.submit-wrap  
  %h4
    %img{class: 'paw', alt: 'paw',
         src: '<%= asset_path("paw28.png") %>'}
    Get your paws on the browser extension or bookmarklet.
  %h6
    The browser extension allows timestamped playback across all supported sites. Please consider installing the extension.

  != JST['tracks/footer']({markletURL : "<%= ENV['markletURL'] %>"})
  
  #how-to
    %h4.tidbit
      <%= image_tag("paw28.png", class: 'paw') %>
      When you hear something you like, click the extension or marklet on the page.

    %p.extension-img-wrap
      <%= image_tag("extension.png", :class => "extension-img") %>

    %h4.tidbit
      <%= image_tag("paw28.png", class: 'paw') %>

      Submit the track at the time you want saved. Visit
      %a{href: "/meow"} stereopaw
      to listen to your tracks, and hear more of the best.

    %p.marklet-img-wrap
      <%= image_tag("marklet.png", :class => "marklet-img", :width => "435px", :height => "274px") %>
